> I have found there is no space for them. On occasion, some people have
> forced them on and they have popped off the lock ring later.

A few years ago I took my shafts and new CV joints to a machinist to have
the CV's pressed on.  The machinist put the dished washers on (I assumed he
knew not to) but I left them in place and never had a hint of trouble.
